(a) The XRD patterns of CH3NH3Pb(BrxI1−x)3 obtained with VHBr% for 0%, 10%, 20%, 40%, 50%, 60%, 80%, and 100%, (b) The XRD patterns of CH3NH3Pb(BrxI1−x)3 magnified in 2θ from 27.5° to 31° (the subscript c is defined as cubic phase, and the subscript t is defined as tetragonal phase).

